#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:2
#: e03c159364984d7da15c46301cfe5a27
msgid "Inverse Design & Identification"
msgstr "反问题设计与辨识"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:4
#: e7cdb61bdd2249289fdc0a0aa7e32f14
msgid ""
"TensorMesh is differentiable end to end: every step of ``Mesh → Assembler → "
"SparseMatrix → Condenser → Solve`` is an ``nn.Module`` or a custom "
"``autograd.Function``, and the linear solve carries an analytic **adjoint "
"backward** (inherited from ``torch-sla``). A loss computed on the FEM "
"solution can therefore be back-propagated to *anything* upstream — a "
"coefficient at every node, a per-element design density, a source term — "
"without writing a single sensitivity equation by hand. The "
":doc:`../user_guide/differentiability` chapter covers the mechanics; this "
"gallery turns it into three runnable scripts in "
"``examples/inverse_design/``."
msgstr ""
"TensorMesh 是端到端可微的：\\ ``Mesh → Assembler → SparseMatrix → Condenser → "
"Solve`` 的每一步都是一个 ``nn.Module`` 或自定义的 ``autograd.Function``\\ ，而线性求解携带了解析的 "
"**伴随反向传播**\\ （继承自 ``torch-sla``\\ ）。因此，在 FEM 解上计算的损失可以反向传播到上游的 *任意* "
"量——每个节点上的系数、逐单元的设计密度、源项——而无需手写哪怕一个灵敏度方程。\\ "
":doc:`../user_guide/differentiability` 一章介绍了其原理；本示例库将其落地为 "
"``examples/inverse_design/`` 中三个可运行的脚本。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:15
#: 94390ac6e2654b00874ab0c58d3adc48
msgid "They span the two flavours of \"gradient through the PDE\":"
msgstr "它们涵盖了\"穿过 PDE 求梯度\"的两种类型："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:17
#: 46ec34ad075c4b1ab533ae258e1c67c5
msgid ""
"**Identification** — recover an unknown field from observations "
"(``coefficient_identification.py``)."
msgstr "**辨识** —— 从观测中恢复一个未知场（\\ ``coefficient_identification.py``\\ ）。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:19
#: 5e7729931f144b5da0c6dd2c4f125025
msgid ""
"**Design** — choose a field that optimises an objective under constraints "
"(``thermal_topology.py`` and ``compliance_topology.py``)."
msgstr ""
"**设计** —— 在约束下选择一个使目标最优的场（\\ ``thermal_topology.py`` 与 "
"``compliance_topology.py``\\ ）。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:24
#: 4ddbba558bfc4973a4ccd1ffa3bd35e3
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"All three obtain their gradients purely from ``autograd``. None of them "
"implements an adjoint by hand — that is the whole point. The classical SIMP "
"sensitivity :math:`\\partial C/\\partial \\rho_e = "
"-p\\,\\rho_e^{p-1}(E_{\\max}-E_{\\min})\\, "
"\\mathbf{u}_e^{T}\\mathbf{K}_0^e\\mathbf{u}_e` falls out of "
"``compliance.backward()`` automatically."
msgstr ""
"这三个示例的梯度全部来自 ``autograd``\\ 。它们都没有手写伴随——这正是关键所在。经典的 SIMP 灵敏度 "
":math:`\\partial C/\\partial \\rho_e = "
"-p\\,\\rho_e^{p-1}(E_{\\max}-E_{\\min})\\, "
"\\mathbf{u}_e^{T}\\mathbf{K}_0^e\\mathbf{u}_e` 会自动地从 "
"``compliance.backward()`` 中得出。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:33
#: b71aae44862642399bd55fd020e78c8f
msgid "Coefficient-field identification — ``coefficient_identification.py``"
msgstr "系数场辨识 —— ``coefficient_identification.py``"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:35
#: 22c53b8b28df4248bf5ec4e8dfed0fc3
msgid ""
"Recover an unknown, spatially varying diffusion coefficient "
":math:`\\kappa(x)` in"
msgstr "在下式中恢复一个未知的、随空间变化的扩散系数 :math:`\\kappa(x)`\\ ："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:38
#: f1f2f95d93464d098b19e3db7a5b393f
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"-\\nabla\\!\\cdot\\!\\big(\\kappa(x)\\,\\nabla u\\big) = f \\quad\\text{in }(0,1)^2,\n"
"\\qquad u = 0 \\text{ on }\\partial\\Omega,"
msgstr ""
"-\\nabla\\!\\cdot\\!\\big(\\kappa(x)\\,\\nabla u\\big) = f \\quad\\text{in }(0,1)^2,\n"
"\\qquad u = 0 \\text{ on }\\partial\\Omega,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:43
#: ddf99ca2807547d985deff321b50306f
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"from a single observed solution :math:`u_{\\rm obs}`. The forward map is "
"\"FEM-solve given :math:`\\kappa`\"; the loss is the L² distance to the "
"observation; Adam descends it. We parametrise :math:`\\kappa = 1 + "
"\\tanh\\theta` so :math:`\\kappa\\in(0,2)` stays strictly positive (the "
"matrix is SPD every iteration) with :math:`\\theta` unconstrained."
msgstr ""
"仅从单个观测解 :math:`u_{\\rm obs}` 出发。前向映射是\"给定 :math:`\\kappa` 后求解 FEM\"；损失是到观测的 "
"L² 距离；由 Adam 进行下降。我们将 :math:`\\kappa = 1 + \\tanh\\theta` 参数化，使得 "
":math:`\\kappa\\in(0,2)` 始终严格为正（矩阵在每次迭代中都是 SPD 的），同时 :math:`\\theta` 不受约束。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:71
#: 4ef85ac741a74e88b864799a25865bb9
msgid ""
"Over 5000 steps the data loss falls by more than seven orders of magnitude "
"and the recovered field matches the four-lobe ground truth almost "
"everywhere:"
msgstr "在 5000 步内，数据损失下降了七个数量级以上，恢复出的场几乎处处与四瓣状的真值相吻合："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:79
#: 413be6ca10a14eb7825bdcce6f9ae188
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Optimisation history: the data loss :math:`\\|u_\\theta - u_{\\rm "
"obs}\\|_2^2` drops to :math:`\\sim 3\\times10^{-10}` (the periodic spikes "
"are Adam overshooting in the ill-conditioned valley, recovered within a few "
"steps); the relative max-norm error in :math:`u` reaches :math:`\\sim "
"6\\times10^{-5}`."
msgstr ""
"优化历史：数据损失 :math:`\\|u_\\theta - u_{\\rm obs}\\|_2^2` 降至 :math:`\\sim "
"3\\times10^{-10}`\\ （周期性的尖峰是 Adam 在病态的谷底过冲所致，几步之内即可恢复）；\\ :math:`u` "
"的相对最大范数误差达到 :math:`\\sim 6\\times10^{-5}`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:90
#: 40e648aa64c8469ea2f96b183788622c
msgid ""
"True (left), recovered (middle), and absolute-error (right) coefficient "
"fields. The only visible residual is a faint blob at the centre, where the "
"constant source makes :math:`\\nabla u` vanish: with no flux there the data "
"barely constrains :math:`\\kappa`, so that region is recovered slowest. A "
"smoothness penalty on :math:`\\theta` removes it."
msgstr ""
"真值（左）、恢复值（中）以及绝对误差（右）的系数场。唯一可见的残差是中心处一个淡淡的斑点，那里常值源使 :math:`\\nabla u` "
"消失：由于该处没有通量，数据几乎无法约束 :math:`\\kappa`\\ ，因此该区域恢复得最慢。对 :math:`\\theta` "
"施加一个光滑性惩罚即可消除它。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:99
#: 99209038cd5e404bac2e16416531ed8b
msgid "Thermal-compliance topology optimization — ``thermal_topology.py``"
msgstr "热柔顺度拓扑优化 —— ``thermal_topology.py``"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:101
#: debcc27b8b254fa1b55a886587c83361
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Distribute a fixed amount of conductive material on the unit square so as to"
" drain heat from a central source to the cold boundary as efficiently as "
"possible — minimise the thermal compliance :math:`J = "
"\\mathbf{b}^{T}\\mathbf{u}` under a hard volume cap:"
msgstr ""
"在单位正方形上分布固定数量的导热材料，使其尽可能高效地将热量从中心源排向冷边界——在硬体积上限约束下最小化热柔顺度 :math:`J = "
"\\mathbf{b}^{T}\\mathbf{u}`\\ ："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:106
#: 5bec896c476c43ada4fdb3e74336e174
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\min_{\\rho}\\;\\; \\mathbf{b}^{T}\\mathbf{u}\n"
"\\quad\\text{s.t.}\\quad\n"
"\\mathbf{K}(\\rho)\\,\\mathbf{u} = \\mathbf{b},\\;\\;\n"
"\\tfrac{1}{|\\Omega|}\\!\\int_\\Omega \\rho \\le V,\\;\\;\n"
"\\rho_{\\min}\\le\\rho\\le 1,"
msgstr ""
"\\min_{\\rho}\\;\\; \\mathbf{b}^{T}\\mathbf{u}\n"
"\\quad\\text{s.t.}\\quad\n"
"\\mathbf{K}(\\rho)\\,\\mathbf{u} = \\mathbf{b},\\;\\;\n"
"\\tfrac{1}{|\\Omega|}\\!\\int_\\Omega \\rho \\le V,\\;\\;\n"
"\\rho_{\\min}\\le\\rho\\le 1,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:114
#: b2269c5cef2c4b36b6d31e6bbf3101ff
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"with a SIMP conductivity law "
":math:`\\kappa(\\rho)=\\kappa_{\\min}+(1-\\kappa_{\\min})\\,\\rho^{p}` and a"
" per-element density :math:`\\rho`. The compliance gradient comes from "
"autograd; the density update is the built-in "
":class:`~tensormesh.optimizer.OCOptimizer` (Optimality Criteria with a "
"volume-bisection step)."
msgstr ""
"其中采用 SIMP 导热率定律 "
":math:`\\kappa(\\rho)=\\kappa_{\\min}+(1-\\kappa_{\\min})\\,\\rho^{p}` "
"以及逐单元密度 :math:`\\rho`\\ 。柔顺度梯度来自自动微分；密度更新使用内置的 "
":class:`~tensormesh.optimizer.OCOptimizer`\\ （带体积二分步的最优准则法）。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:142
#: ef11c12d48ba4d9499287db8d47f072e
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The optimal layout is a \"thermal cross\" connecting the hot centre to the "
"four cold mid-edges; compliance drops about :math:`8.6\\times` "
"(:math:`5.9\\times10^{-3} \\to 6.9\\times10^{-4}`) while the volume fraction"
" is held at :math:`0.4` exactly:"
msgstr ""
"最优布局是一个\"热十字\"，将炽热的中心与四条冷的边中点相连；柔顺度下降了约 :math:`8.6\\times`\\ （\\ "
":math:`5.9\\times10^{-3} \\to 6.9\\times10^{-4}`\\ ），同时体积分数被精确地保持在 "
":math:`0.4`\\ ："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:151
#: c24f51477c2a4ff2aea5f4493519bb55
msgid ""
"Density evolution over 60 OC steps (iteration 0 is the uniform :math:`\\rho "
"= V` start) and the compliance history. The cross has emerged by iteration 5"
" and sharpens into a near 0/1 design by the end."
msgstr ""
"60 个 OC 步内的密度演化（第 0 次迭代是均匀的 :math:`\\rho = V` 初始值）以及柔顺度历史。十字结构在第 5 "
"次迭代时已经显现，并在结尾处锐化为接近 0/1 的设计。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:156
#: efccc60c8fd54e02b5ef64cf163d7b7b
msgid ""
"This is the scalar/heat counterpart of the structural problem below: "
"identical \"autograd sensitivity + density update\" pattern, different "
"physics and a different optimiser."
msgstr "这是下面结构问题的标量/热学对应版本：相同的\"自动微分灵敏度 + 密度更新\"模式，不同的物理与不同的优化器。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:162
#: b5610d65f490449e8d5f9f6b88e8ebba
msgid ""
"Structural compliance topology optimization — ``compliance_topology.py``"
msgstr "结构柔顺度拓扑优化 —— ``compliance_topology.py``"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:164
#: b826ea018203488eaca2cee09bc47256
msgid ""
"The classical 2D cantilever: minimise structural compliance under a volume "
"constraint, **SIMP** density interpolation, **MMA** (Method of Moving "
"Asymptotes) updates with a density filter. It is set up to match a JAX-FEM "
"reference problem for a head-to-head comparison."
msgstr ""
"经典的二维悬臂梁：在体积约束下最小化结构柔顺度，采用 **SIMP** 密度插值、带密度滤波的 **MMA**\\ "
"（移动渐近线法）更新。它被配置为与一个 JAX-FEM 参考问题相匹配，以便进行正面对比。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:173
#: b8b631bf7356426cacb71c2a2b8aebc0
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**Setup.** Domain :math:`60\\times30` with :math:`60\\times30` QUAD4 "
"elements (1891 nodes, 1800 elements); left edge clamped "
"(:math:`\\mathbf{u}=\\mathbf{0}` at :math:`x=0`); a downward traction "
":math:`\\mathbf{t}=[0,-100]^{T}` on the bottom-right corner; plane-stress "
"material with :math:`E_{\\max}=70\\,000`, :math:`E_{\\min}=70`, "
":math:`\\nu=0.3`, SIMP penalty :math:`p=3`, target volume fraction "
":math:`\\bar v = 0.5`."
msgstr ""
"**设置。** 区域为 :math:`60\\times30`\\ ，剖分为 :math:`60\\times30` 个 QUAD4 单元（1891 "
"个节点，1800 个单元）；左边固支（在 :math:`x=0` 处 :math:`\\mathbf{u}=\\mathbf{0}`\\ "
"）；右下角施加向下的面力 :math:`\\mathbf{t}=[0,-100]^{T}`\\ ；平面应力材料，\\ "
":math:`E_{\\max}=70\\,000`\\ 、\\ :math:`E_{\\min}=70`\\ 、\\ "
":math:`\\nu=0.3`\\ ，SIMP 惩罚系数 :math:`p=3`\\ ，目标体积分数 :math:`\\bar v = 0.5`\\ "
"。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/inverse_design.rst:181
#: dc14c73eb4dc4dafa7d98f5988384446
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\min_{\\rho}\\; C(\\rho) = \\mathbf{u}^{T}\\mathbf{K}(\\rho)\\,\\mathbf{u}\n"
"\\quad\\text{s.t.}\\quad\n"
"\\mathbf{K}(\\rho)\\mathbf{u} = \\mathbf{F},\\;\\;\n"
"\\tfrac{1}{|\\Omega|}\\!\\int_\\Omega\\rho \\le \\bar v,\\;\\;\n"
"0 < \\rho_{\\min}\\le\\rho\\le 1,\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"E(\\rho) = E_{\\min} + \\rho^{p}\\,(E_{\\max}-E_{\\min})."
msgstr ""
"\\min_{\\rho}\\; C(\\rho) = \\mathbf{u}^{T}\\mathbf{K}(\\rho)\\,\\mathbf{u}\n"
"\\quad\\text{s.t.}\\quad\n"
"\\mathbf{K}(\\rho)\\mathbf{u} = \\mathbf{F},\\;\\;\n"
"\\tfrac{1}{|\\Omega|}\\!\\int_\\Omega\\rho \\le \\bar v,\\;\\;\n"
"0 < \\rho_{\\min}\\le\\rho\\le 1,\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"E(\\rho) = E_{\\min} + \\rho^{p}\\,(E_{\\max}-E_{\\min})."

